Steps to add buttons
	1. Copy the play_btn entitiy
	2. Create a new entitiy
		change name
		change class name example "play_btn": true
		change image name
	3. Write Scripts
		create the new script in simulation
		copy from start.js
		rename it to the name of the button we are creating
		change the data.switchScene to whatever the scene we are adding it to
	4. Add it to systems.json
		copy start
		in the scene add the name of the scene it will be in
